### Request

Something like:

```graphql
{
  geoNode {
    packageFileRegistries {
      nodes {
        id
        packageFileId
        state
        retryCount
        lastSyncFailure
        retryAt
        lastSyncedAt
        createdAt
      }
    }
  }
}
```

